                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Griscom</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-11-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(The inauguration, November 15, of Affonso Penna as President and the
                    continuation of Baron Rio Branco as minister for foreign affairs are
                    reported.)</p>
            </div>
